@[simp]
theorem linear_map.to_matrix_transpose (u : «expr →ₗ[ ] » V₁ K V₂) :
    linear_map.to_matrix B₂.dual_basis B₁.dual_basis (module.dual.transpose u) =
      matrix.transpose (linear_map.to_matrix B₁ B₂ u) :=
  by
  ext (i j)
  simp only [linear_map.to_matrix_apply, module.dual.transpose_apply, B₁.dual_basis_repr, B₂.dual_basis_apply,
    matrix.transpose_apply, linear_map.comp_apply]
#align linear_map.to_matrix_transpose linear_map.to_matrix_transpose
to_lin_transpose:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.transpose -/
@[simp]
theorem matrix.to_lin_transpose (M : matrix ι₁ ι₂ K) :
    matrix.to_lin B₁.dual_basis B₂.dual_basis (matrix.transpose M) = module.dual.transpose (matrix.to_lin B₂ B₁ M) :=
  by
  apply (linear_map.to_matrix B₁.dual_basis B₂.dual_basis).injective
  rw [linear_map.to_matrix_to_lin, linear_map.to_matrix_transpose, linear_map.to_matrix_to_lin]
#align matrix.to_lin_transpose matrix.to_lin_transpose
